uis-Marie de Jonghe d'Ardoye]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|BEL|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Gigolo\n|-\n|align=left|[[Binder Ott\u00f3]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|HUN|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Jukker\n|-\n|align=left|[[Victor Ankarcrona]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|SWE|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Mascha\n|-\n|align=left|[[Charles George (equestrian)|Charles George]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|USA|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Ozella\n|-\n|align=left|[[E. M. Longin Spindler]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|FRA|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Poup\u00e9e\n|-\n|align=left|[[Francisco Gim\u00e9nez]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|ESP|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Quart d'heure\n|-\n|align=left|[[Georges Van der Ton]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|BEL|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Remember Erin\n|-\n|align=left|[[Angelio Somalo]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|ESP|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Royal\n|-\n|align=left|[[Ren\u00e9 de Ribeaupierre]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|SUI|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Sergent\n|-\n|align=left|[[Tommaso Lequio di Assaba]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|ITA|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Uroski\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n{{Olympic champions \u2013 Equestrian individual eventing}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Equestrian At The 1928 Summer Olympics - Eventing Individual}}\n[[Category:Equestrian at the 1928 Summer Olympics]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Equestrian at the Olympics}}\n{{Infobox Olympic event\n|event = Individual eventing\n|games = 1928 Summer\n|image = \n|caption = \n|venue = [[Hilversum]]\n|date = \n|competitors = 46\n|nations = 17\n|win_value = \n|gold = [[Charles Pahud de Mortanges]] and Marcroix\n|goldNOC = NED\n|silver = [[Gerard de Kruijff]] and Va-T'en\n|silverNOC = NED\n|bronze = [[Bruno Neumann]] and Ilja\n|bronzeNOC = GER\n|prev= [[Equestrian at the 1924 Summer Olympics \u2013 Individual eventing|1924]]\n|next= [[Equestrian at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Individual eventing|1932]]\n}}\n{{EquestrianAt1928SummerOlympics}}\n\nThe '''individual eventing''' at the '''[[1928 Summer Olympics]]''' (referred to at the time as the \"competition for the equestrian championship\") took place at [[Hilversum]].  The event consisted of a dressage competition, a jumping competition, and an endurance test.  Scores in each component were added to give a total.\n\nScores from the individual competition were summed to give results in the [[Equestrian at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Team eventing|team competition]].\n\n==Results==\nSource: Official results;<ref name=overallresults>{{cite web|url=http://www.la84foundation.org/6oic/OfficialReports/1928/1928.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080408184510/http://www.la84foundation.org/6oic/OfficialReports/1928/1928.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-date=2008-04-08 |title=1928 Summer Olympics official report }}</ref> De Wael<ref name=hdw>{{cite web|url=http://users.skynet.be/hermandw/olymp/equ1928.html |title=Equestrianism 1928}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!Rank\n!Rider\n!Nation\n!Horse\n!Total Score\n\n|-\n!{{gold01}}\n|align=left|[[Charles Pahud de Mortanges]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|NED|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Marcroix\n|1969.82\n|-\n!{{silver02}}\n|align=left|[[Gerard de Kruijff]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|NED|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Va-t-en\n|1967.26\n|-\n!{{bronze03}}\n|align=left|[[Bruno Neumann]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|GER|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Ilja\n|1944.42\n|-\n!4\n|align=left|[[Adolf van der Voort van Zijp]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|NED|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Silver Piece\n|1928.60\n|-\n!5\n|align=left|[[Hans Olof von Essen]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|FIN|1928 Summer}}||align=left|El Kaid\n|1924.64\n|-\n!6\n|align=left|[[Bjart Ording]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|NOR|1928 Summer}}||align=left|And Over\n|1912.98\n|-\n!7\n|align=left|[[Nils Kettner]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|SWE|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Caesar\n|1901.66\n|-\n!8\n|align=left|[[Arthur Qvist]]||align=left|{{flagIOC|NOR|1928 Summer}}||align=left|Hidalgo\n|1895.14\n|-\n!9\n|align=left|[[Peder Jensen (equestrian)|Peder Jensen]